<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>وَجَرَّ زَعِيمُ الْقَوْمِ لِلتُّرْكِ دَوْلَةً<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>عَلَى مِلَّةِ الإِسْلامِ فِعْلَ الْمُكَابِرِ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وَوَازَرَهُ فِي رَأْيِهِ كُلُّ جَاهِل<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>يَرُوحُ وَيَغْدُو آثِماً غَيْرَ شَاكِرِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>وَآخَر يَبْتَاعُ الضَّلالةَ بِالْهُدَى<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>وَيَخْتَالُ فِي ثَوْبٍ مِنْ الْكِبْرِ وَافِرِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>وَثَالِثُهُمْ لا يَعْبُؤُ الدَّهْرِ بِالَّتِي<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>تَبِيدُ مِنْ الإِسْلامِ عَزْمَ الْمَذَاكِرِ<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَلَكِنَّهُ يَهْوَى وَيَعْمَلُ لِلْهَوَى<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وَيُصْبِحُ فِي بَحْرٍ مِنْ الرَّيْبِ عَامِرِ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَقَدْ جَاءَكُمْ فِيمَا مَضَى خَيْرُ نَاصِحٍ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>إِمَامُ هُدىً يَبْنِي رَفِيعَ الْمَفَاخِرِ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>وَيُنْقِذُهُمْ مِنْ قَعْرِ ظَلْمَا مُضِّلِّةٍ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>لِسَالِكِهَا أَوْ مِنْ لَظَى وَالْمَسَاعِرِ<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>وَيُخْبِرُهُمْ أَنَّ السَّلامَةَ فِي الَّتِي<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>عَلَيْهَاَ خِيَارُ الصَّحْبِ مِنْ كُلِّ شَاكِرِ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>فَلَمَّا أَتَاهُمْ نَصْرُ ذِي الْعَرْشِ وَاحْتَوَى<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>أَكَابِرُهُمْ كَنْزَ اللُّهَى وَالذَّخَائِرِ<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>سَعَوْا جُهْدَهُمْ فِي هَدْمِ مَا قَدْ بَنَى لَهُمْ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>مَشَائِخُهُمْ وَاسْتَنْصَرُوا كُلَّ دَاغر<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>